@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs:    <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix owl:     <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>.
@prefix : <http://example.org/>.

:MyConcept rdf:type skos:Concept, owl:Class, owl:ObjectProperty .
:MyConcept skos:inScheme :MyScheme.
:MyConcept skos:topConceptOf :MyScheme.

:MyScheme rdf:type skos:ConceptScheme, owl:Class, owl:ObjectProperty.

:MyScheme skos:hasTopConcept :MyConcept.
